  "description": "Add meme to villager trade GUI",
  "body": "# A tiny resource pack that adds the \"No emeralds?\" meme into your game GUI\n### No emeralds?\n![NO EMERALDS?](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/LmVAy4RR/images/578951ca4342526b96c47907d0cfb7def13ca90e.png)\n\n## Features\n- Replaces only the villagers trade interface,\n- Compatible with other GUI resourcespacks (should be at the top of the list),\n- Compatible with 1.14 and above,\n- _NO EMERALDS?_.\n\n## Notes\n- This pack is purely visual and does **not affect gameplay**,\n- Safe to use on servers,\n- Perfect for meme lovers or lighthearted modpacks.\n\n## For Modpack Creators\n- I allow this resource pack to be used in modpacks.",
